TITLE: Using Stealth Plugin with Custom Options in Playwright
DESCRIPTION: Example of using the stealth plugin with playwright-extra and custom options for evasion techniques.
SOURCE: https://github.com/berstend/puppeteer-extra/blob/master/packages/playwright-extra/readme.md#2025-04-23_snippet_8

